    <item>
      <title>以色列避开伊朗袭击能源目标，欧洲天然气供应下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/europe-gas-slips-as-israel-avoids-energy-targets-in-iran-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对伊朗目标的袭击避开了石油、核能和民用基础设施，导致欧洲天然气价格下跌，表明与中东冲突相关的供应风险目前仍在控制之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/europe-gas-slips-as-israel-avoids-energy-targets-in-iran-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 07:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国被动股票资产首次超过主动股票资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/passive-equity-assets-in-china-exceed-active-ones-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被动型基金管理的中国股票规模已经超过主动型基金管理的股票规模，这是中国迅速赶上全球被动型基金热潮的一个重要里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/passive-equity-assets-in-china-exceed-active-ones-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 03:40:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
